{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2023/08/27/support/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bono blog","author":"bono"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d23ce472-b1f3-594f-af50-167b388fdfb2","excerpt":"웹 디자인 및 개발에서 크로스 브라우저 호환성은 항상 큰 주제입니다. CSS의  규칙은 이 문제를 해결하는 데 큰 도움을 줍니다. 이 규칙을 사용하면 특정 CSS 기능이 브라우저에 의해 지원되는지 여부를 확인하고 조건부로 스타일을 적용할 수 있습니다…","html":"<p>웹 디자인 및 개발에서 크로스 브라우저 호환성은 항상 큰 주제입니다. CSS의 <code class=\"language-text\">@supports</code> 규칙은 이 문제를 해결하는 데 큰 도움을 줍니다. 이 규칙을 사용하면 특정 CSS 기능이 브라우저에 의해 지원되는지 여부를 확인하고 조건부로 스타일을 적용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"supports란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#supports%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"supports란 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>@supports란?</strong></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">@supports</code> 규칙은 CSS의 기능 쿼리입니다. 이는 미디어 쿼리와 유사하지만, 화면 크기나 장치 유형 대신 CSS 속성 및 값의 지원 여부를 테스트합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"기본-사용법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"기본 사용법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>기본 사용법</strong></h3>\n<p>기본적인 사용법은 다음과 같습니다:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@supports</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* 그리드 레이아웃을 지원하는 브라우저에만 적용될 스타일 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 예에서, 브라우저가 <code class=\"language-text\">display: grid</code>를 지원하는 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">.container</code>에 그리드 레이아웃 스타일이 적용됩니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"조건-연산자-활용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%9E%90-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"조건 연산자 활용 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>조건 연산자 활용</strong></h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">and</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">or</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">not</code>와 같은 논리 연산자를 사용하여 복잡한 조건을 만들 수 있습니다:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@supports</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> and <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">grid-gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"supports-활용-사례\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#supports-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9-%EC%82%AC%EB%A1%80\" aria-label=\"supports 활용 사례 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>@supports 활용 사례</strong></h3>\n<h4 id=\"그리드-레이아웃-백업-스타일\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%AC%EB%93%9C-%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%95%84%EC%9B%83-%EB%B0%B1%EC%97%85-%EC%8A%A4%ED%83%80%EC%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"그리드 레이아웃 백업 스타일 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>그리드 레이아웃 백업 스타일</strong></h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">@supports</code>를 사용하면 그리드 레이아웃이 지원되지 않는 브라우저에 대한 백업 스타일을 제공할 수 있습니다:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@supports</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.container</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"변수fonts-colors-등-사용-가능-여부-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98fonts-colors-%EB%93%B1-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5-%EC%97%AC%EB%B6%80-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"변수fonts colors 등 사용 가능 여부 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>변수(fonts, colors 등) 사용 가능 여부 확인</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@supports</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--main-color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--main-color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"주의사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"주의사항 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>주의사항</strong></h3>\n<p>모든 브라우저가 <code class=\"language-text\">@supports</code> 규칙을 지원하지는 않습니다. 그러나 대부분의 최신 브라우저는 지원하며, 이 규칙을 지원하지 않는 브라우저에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">@supports</code> 블록 내의 스타일을 단순히 무시하게 됩니다. 따라서 그 자체로 안전하게 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d68b27e1462f4bba6cf6f8f0c622ea3a/ac307/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.86486486486486%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"CSS Feature Queries\"\n        title=\"CSS Feature Queries\"\n        src=\"/static/d68b27e1462f4bba6cf6f8f0c622ea3a/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d68b27e1462f4bba6cf6f8f0c622ea3a/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/d68b27e1462f4bba6cf6f8f0c622ea3a/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/d68b27e1462f4bba6cf6f8f0c622ea3a/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/d68b27e1462f4bba6cf6f8f0c622ea3a/efc66/1.png 885w,\n/static/d68b27e1462f4bba6cf6f8f0c622ea3a/c83ae/1.png 1180w,\n/static/d68b27e1462f4bba6cf6f8f0c622ea3a/ac307/1.png 2058w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/css-featurequeries\">CSS Feature Queries</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2023/08/27/support/#supports%EB%9E%80\"><strong>@supports란?</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2023/08/27/support/#%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\"><strong>기본 사용법</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2023/08/27/support/#%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%9E%90-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9\"><strong>조건 연산자 활용</strong></a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/2023/08/27/support/#supports-%ED%99%9C%EC%9A%A9-%EC%82%AC%EB%A1%80\"><strong>@supports 활용 사례</strong></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2023/08/27/support/#%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%AC%EB%93%9C-%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%95%84%EC%9B%83-%EB%B0%B1%EC%97%85-%EC%8A%A4%ED%83%80%EC%9D%BC\"><strong>그리드 레이아웃 백업 스타일</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2023/08/27/support/#%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98fonts-colors-%EB%93%B1-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5-%EC%97%AC%EB%B6%80-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\"><strong>변수(fonts, colors 등) 사용 가능 여부 확인</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/2023/08/27/support/#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\"><strong>주의사항</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2023/08/27/support/#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\">참고</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[CSS] @supports, 브라우저 지원 기능 조건에 따라 스타일 적용하기","date":"2023-08-27"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2023/08/27/support/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2023/08/26/design-pattern-for-frontend/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"프론트엔드(frontend) 마스터를 위한 디자인 패턴 적용 가이드","tags":["javascript","front-end","design-pattern"]}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}